data.description: WOW!! All this house! This great 5 bedroom (potential 6) home is in the beautiful Sorrento neighborhood, and is ready for its new owners! This home sits in the back of a cul-da-sac, with a fully fenced in back yard. Inside you wont be disappointed with the amount of space. The split floor plan has the primary bedroom on 1 side of the home and 2 additional bedrooms on the other side that have a jack and jill full bathroom. The HUGE kitchen boasts floor to ceiling windows and 9 foot ceilings, with a 2 way fireplace.  The Kitchen walks out to the back deck, that wraps around to the primary bedroom.  In the basement you will find new carpet, kitchenette, bonus living space, full bathroom, 2 bedrooms and an additional room. Plenty of closet space for storage as well. You can walk straight outside from your basement and enjoy your covered patio area.
